The '''cinnamon-breasted warbler''' or '''kopje warbler''' ('''''Euryptila subcinnamomea''''') is a species of bird in the family [[Cisticolidae]]. It is the only species placed in the genus '''''Euryptila'''''.<ref name = "ITIS"/> It is found in [[Namibia]] and [[South Africa]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is [[subtropical or tropical dry shrubland]].

